ACCESSIBILITY NOTES

Color Contrast

• Maintain minimum contrast ratio of 4.5:1.

Typography

• Minimum body text size should be 16px.

Touch Targets

• Buttons should have a minimum size of 44 × 44 px.

Keyboard Navigation

• All interactive elements should be keyboard accessible.

Forms

• Inputs must contain labels and error messages.

Alt Text

• Images and icons should include descriptive labels.

Consistency

• Avoid using color alone to communicate information.
